## Schema

### Required

- `app_id` (String) The ID of the Okta Application.

### Optional

- `id` (String) Push Group ID
- `source_group_id` (String) The ID of the source group in Okta.

### Read-Only

- `status` (String) The status of the push group mapping. Valid values: `ACTIVE` and `INACTIVE`
- `target_group_id` (String) The ID of the existing target group for the push group mapping. This is used to link to an existing group
